<br>
Then sell your full charged Golem wand to the merchant, after its sold, you will see it on merchant, then sell your empty wands, then buy them all back.<br>
<br>
Just make sure you sell the full charged wand first.<br>
<br>
This cost about 120pp per wand, so say you have 5 wands, 4 empty and 1 full, it will cost you 600pp to recharge. Well worth it, if you pvp.<br>
